document.title: Muziekopnamen Zendgemachtigden
document.intro: Selection from the Sound & Vision open data catalog that is registered under the series Music recordings broadcasting agents (MOZ). This selection can be queried from the contentUrl using this query: https://cat.apis.beeldengeluid.nl/sparql?query=PREFIX%20sdo%3A%20%3Chttps%3A//schema.or... Original concert and studio recordings made by public broadcasters. Integral recordings across many genres.
